# CODEOWNERS — defense-in-depth for publishing-adjacent paths.
#
# Even if a bot workflow (Claude, Renovate, etc.) successfully pushes a change
# to any of these paths via prompt injection or a compromised dependency, the
# PR cannot merge without owner approval. Pairs with the protected-paths
# stanza in .github/workflows/claude*.yml (the first line of defense).
#
# See /harden-image-pipeline skill: "Protecting the publish pipeline from
# bot workflows" and /ci-workflow skill: "Claude-Powered Workflow Security".

# CI / CD infrastructure
.github/workflows/**        @AndriyKalashnykov
.github/actions/**          @AndriyKalashnykov
